  "text": "Ionic liquids and indium metal were purchased from commercial sources and used as received. N-Benzylcinchonidium bromide was prepared according to the literature [CITATION_1] . Allylic bromides and aldehydes were distilled just before use. All reactions were carried out under argon.",
